lead_paragraph: Short-handed No. 15 SMU can make a lot of 3-pointers and also put on quite a show with alley-oop passes that lead to rim-rattling dunks. Except those plays don't generally go hand-in-hand.

headline.print_headline: Short-Handed No. 15 SMU Still Undefeated, Beats UCF 88-73
